Message:
We are very excited to announce that for the first time ever, our music will be be transformed into an original musical:

 AQUA THE MUSICAL ??

We’ve had a wild ride, full of experiences that have never been told before. Now, we’re incredibly excited to relive them as a musical, together with the rest of the world. We’re certain it will be both fun and moving, and at the same time a reminder of everything we’ve been through and how privileged we’ve been. If the team manage to capture just a fraction of what it felt like, we can promise it will be entertaining ✨

The show is produced by the Danish production company @AHA Creations and the world premiere will take place in Copenhagen in 2028. 

